**Pivot Idea: AI Resume Review & Optimization Tool**

---

## 🚀 Overview
Build an AI-powered tool that helps job seekers fix their resumes so they get noticed by recruiters and beat the ATS (Applicant Tracking System) filters. It will:
- Review uploaded resumes
- Provide personalized, actionable feedback
- Offer ATS-friendly templates
- Optionally generate resumes from scratch

---

## 📈 Why This Pivot Works
**Market Demand:** Millions of job seekers globally struggle with resume writing
**Pain Point:** Most resumes are poorly written, not optimized for ATS, and cause people to miss interviews
**AI Edge:** Smart, role-specific feedback and generation at scale
**Monetization Potential:** High — people will pay to increase their chances of landing a job

---

## 📊 Target Users
- Students & fresh grads
- Mid-career professionals switching jobs
- Freelancers building a more corporate presence
- Immigrants or remote workers applying globally

---

## 🛠️ Core Features (MVP)

### 1. Resume Review Engine
- Upload a resume (PDF/DOCX)
- AI analyzes and scores:
  - Structure & readability
  - Grammar & tone
  - ATS compatibility
  - Job-fit score (optional: upload job description too)

### 2. Personalized Suggestions
- Rewrite weak bullets with stronger action verbs
- Keyword optimization for ATS
- Formatting guidance (one-page limit, font size, spacing)

### 3. Resume Templates
- Clean, ATS-friendly templates
- Role-specific formats (Tech, Marketing, Sales, Entry-Level, etc.)
- Export as PDF or Word

### 4. Optional Generator
- Prompt-based resume builder ("What role are you applying for?")
- Let AI generate resume based on experience input

---

## 💰 Monetization Options
| Model | Details |
|-------|---------|
| Freemium | 1 resume review + 1 template for free |
| Pro Plan | $7-10/mo: Unlimited reviews, templates, generation |
| One-time Pay | $5 per AI resume fix |
| Bundle | Resume + Cover Letter + LinkedIn rewrite: $12-15 |

---

## 🔄 Tech Stack Suggestions
- React (frontend)
- Supabase or Firebase (auth & DB)
- Express/NestJS (backend)
- OpenAI GPT-4 (resume feedback engine)
- PDF.js or similar for parsing resumes

---

## 🔧 What You Should Learn First
- ATS systems & how they parse resumes
- Recruiter behavior: what they skim & ignore
- Resume writing best practices
- Clean, minimal template design principles
- How to prompt GPT for resume feedback & rewriting

---

## 🎉 Viral Marketing Hooks
- "Your resume is why you're not getting interviews. Let AI fix it."
- "Built a resume in 60 seconds with AI and landed 3 interviews."
- "Recruiters spend 6 seconds per resume. We show you what they see."

---

